{"word":"G686 - ἄρα - ára - ar'-ah - Haply","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄρα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ára"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ar'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Haply"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஆதலால், எப்படிப்பட்ட, ஆகிலும், அல்லவா - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"under these circumstances something either is so or becomes so"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from <a href=\"#/G142 - αἴρω - aírō - ah'-ee-ro/142\">G142</a> (through the idea of <i>drawing</i> a conclusion); a particle denoting an <i>inference</i> more or less decisive (as follows): - haply, (what) manner (of man), no doubt, perhaps, so be, then, therefore, truly, wherefore. Often used in connection with other particles, especially <a href=\"#/G1065 - γέ - gé - gheh/1065\">G1065</a> or <a href=\"#/G3767 - οὖν - oûn - oon/3767\">G3767</a> (after) or <a href=\"#/G1487 - εἰ - ei - i/1487\">G1487</a> (before). Compare also <a href=\"#/G687 - ἆρα - âra - ar'-ah/687\">G687</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1944 - ἐπικατάρατος - epikatáratos - ep-ee-kat-ar'-at-os/1944\">G1944</a>, <a href=\"#/G2671 - κατάρα - katára - kat-ar'-ah/2671\">G2671</a>, <a href=\"#/G2672 - καταράομαι - kataráomai - kat-ar-ah'-om-ahee/2672\">G2672</a>, <a href=\"#/G685 - ἀρά - ará - ar-ah'/685\">G685</a>, <a href=\"#/G686 - ἄρα - ára - ar'-ah/686\">G686</a>, <a href=\"#/G687 - ἆρα - âra - ar'-ah/687\">G687</a>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}